        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer26347405" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10961848197879410073">I have read this set half a dozen times -- for a while there I re-read them every summer. Foote was a novelist before he was a historian, and it shows in his style. The books give a fairly even-handed treatment of the military history of the American civil war, using actual quotes to flesh out the interactions among the characters to a surprising extent. One of the best histories I&apos;ve ever read. </span>
  <span id="freeText10961848197879410073" style="display:none">I have read this set half a dozen times -- for a while there I re-read them every summer. Foote was a novelist before he was a historian, and it shows in his style. The books give a fairly even-handed treatment of the military history of the American civil war, using actual quotes to flesh out the interactions among the characters to a surprising extent. One of the best histories I've ever read. </span>
